496
00:23:19,458 --> 00:23:21,125
[YURI] This may be a resort,
but it's still winter.

497
00:23:21,208 --> 00:23:22,833
[VICTOR] Oh, right.
It's almost Christmas.

498
00:23:22,916 --> 00:23:24,166
What are you going
to give me, Yuri?

499
00:23:24,250 --> 00:23:25,833
[YURI]
Something round and golden.

500
00:23:25,916 --> 00:23:26,750
[VICTOR]
Wow!

501
00:23:26,833 --> 00:23:27,666
[YURI]
Next time, Tenth Skate:.

502
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:28,916
[VICTOR]
"Gotta Supercharge It!

